How to compile:
gcc infoli.c main.c -o infoli -lm
[-O3, -O2 or -O1] to optimize code for faster execution
[-D NO_OUTPUT] to disable printing detailed information and to disable printing the information to an output to a file (named InferiorOlive_Output.txt)
[-fopenmp] to run with multiple cores (timing measurements will not be accurate)

How to run:
./infoli <network_size> <simulation_steps>

